🍉️1.creating the enum datatype.
  --> create type mood as ENUM('sad','ok','happy');

🍉️2.creating the table for above datatype.
  --> create table person(
	name, text,
	current_mood mood);

🍉️3.Inserting the data into table.
  --> insert into person values('vikas', 'happy'),('vishal','sad');

🍉️4.Using order by clause.
  -->select * from person order by current_mood DESC;
